channel.title: [New]{Hamachi} 508-650 based | Hydroque Land | Full Specs | Godwars
channel.description:
[font=courier]Welcome to my server page here on Moparscape![/font]
Just to say I am not a 24/7 server but my uptime is like 12/7.
This is under development by me as we speak and is super playable. This server revolves around PKing, PvNPC, Minigames (A lot work), and Bossing.
Totally nice Owner and has a few people playing. Full specs are included and very much good animations. (Barely any bug)
Full godwars dungeons
Hamachis: (Reserve only one slot) CodyRSPS_1 CodyRSPS_2 CodyRSPS_3 CodyRSPS_4 CodyRSPS_5
Passwords: 123 :|
Totally active and is changing!
Credits to Paul for his source... A lot of bug fixes towards me.
All potions work. Some armor needs tweaked to original strength.
Downloadable Client. (I have added .bat files for jre6-jre7 on 32 bit and 64 bit)
Client has World Map and Item List installed!
Server is waiting! Come be a pseudo part of my community!
Forums: http://hydroland.free-forums.biz/
Client Download: http://www.mediafire.com/download/3u2kbdcbt42slut/Hydroque_Land_Client.7z
(Pictures to come soon)
